    "---\n",
    "## 3. Training\n",
    "\n",
    "Train the model for `num_runs` seeds. All runs share the same data split; only model initialisation varies. We collect per-run degree-wise accuracy for boxplot distributions.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "e9dee1c89b28",
   "metadata": {},
